description.narrative: The purpose of the Middle East Bureau Support contract is to provide analytical support and technical assistance services to USAID's Middle East (ME) Bureau. The Contractor shall provide technical and other specialists to meet short to medium-term requirements that allow USAID to respond to evolving programs of national priority and address key Administration goals. Specialists shall provide technical assistance related to program design, program management, program monitoring, outreach and information development, and associated administrative support activities.
